title: Networking Strategies That Put You On Top With Ben Gothard
itunes:title: Networking Strategies That Put You On Top With Ben Gothard
description:
I’m sure you’ve heard it before, your network determines your net worth. It’s true.
 
I’d even say that relationships is life’s third most valuable asset next to time and health.
 
Ben Gothard is the host of The Project EGG Show and has built a powerful brand by networking like a gangster.
 
In this interview, we break down how to grow your network to play with the big dawgs and beef up your bankroll.
